messages.title: A Strong Voice for Shrewsbury
messages.content: Hardworking local Lib Dem Christine Tinker is pushing the Conservatives hard as the election battle hots up in Shrewsbury & Atcham.

mentions.tacticalSituation: It's Tinker or the Tories here!

issues.economy: "We CAN have a stronger economy without the Conservatives' cuts for the sake of cuts. We need a new MP who'll fight for a fairer Shrewsbury."

endorsements.endorsement: "This election is wide open. People want change - Christine's determination is making an impact. It's between her and the Conservative."

images.caption: Christine Tinker A Strong Voice for Shrewsbury
